&lt;li&gt;Manage pipeline upkeep and administrative follow-up to help protect opportunity flow and conversion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support advisor match and routing to help ensure timely response and appropriate lead handling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a backup resource for inbound FC calls and support, as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate Financial Planning Group (FPG) proposal requests and other sales support tasks that advance opportunities efficiently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage wholesaling and FC-facing email support to improve responsiveness and consistency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Protect speed-to-lead and overall responsiveness across the market through disciplined task execution and follow-up.&lt;/li&gt;
